# tools/check_plan_data_sync.py hashes the Plan Data CSVs byte-for-byte
# (hashlib.sha256(path.read_bytes())) against input/plan_data_manifest.json.
# Without an explicit policy, Git's core.autocrlf converts LF -> CRLF on
# checkout on Windows, changing every byte count and SHA256 versus the
# manifest recorded on a Linux/Mac checkout. Force LF everywhere so the
# checked-out bytes are identical across platforms and CI runners.
*.csv text eol=lf
input/plan_data_manifest.json text eol=lf
